cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL

The paper deals with data augmentation techniques for improving the accuracy of classification results, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The proposed algorithm involves searching for the best augmentation policies, which can also be relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL) where data augmentation is used to increase the size of training data.
